Package main

Class Employee

java.lang.Object
main.Employee
Direct Known Subclasses:
FullTimeEmployee, PartTimeEmployee
public abstract class Employee extends Object

The Employee class serves as an abstract base class for different types of employees. It contains common fields and methods shared across various employee types, such as ID, name, department, and role. Subclasses must implement the abstract methods to define specific behaviors for clocking in, clocking out, and tracking work hours.

Since:
1.0
Author:
DanialSamadi
